text: Reimu Hakurei: I'm pretty sure you are behind this party...
Yukari Yakumo: That's right. So much fun, right?
Reimu Hakurei: I will stop you, you are annoying me for way too long...
Yukari Yakumo: You may yeet more yankees, but may I use your ball?
Yukari Yakumo: An alliteration, or sound combo for you.
Yukari Yakumo: Since you do neat combos with your balls, I can do the same with words
Reimu Hakurei: Heh... Come and taste my ball!
Yukari Yakumo: Your ball... A rock, a stone, a dust... Let me show it to you.
Yukari Yakumo: I will happily continue to play with you!
Reimu Hakurei: You won't stop me! It's over now!
Yukari Yakumo: You are an annoying fun, you know!
Reimu Hakurei: Darn! Stop it with your word combos!
Reimu Hakurei: Taste my ball combos instead!
